{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Me, You and Kaiju, battle against your friends in an action-packed, asymmetric, local-multiplayer party game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you step into VR as the mighty Kaiju to wreak havoc &amp; squash your puny friends? Or will you pick up a controller, jump in a chopper and take to the skies with your buddies to take down the Kaiju and save Earth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Up to 4 players can grab a gamepad and play split screen against the VR-controlled Kaiju</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take control of various different vehicles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse the level, flanking the Kaiju, while dodging the onslaught of attacks it\u2019s throwing at you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help your buddies by manning the gunner seat of their vehicles.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092200/extras/Kaiju_Gif.gif?t=1728016255\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092200/extras/Grabhelicpoter.gif?t=1728016255\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Take control of the kaiju and experience being a giant in VR</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your surroundings as ammunition</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dodge and block projectiles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your special attack to unleash havoc across the city</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as different kaiju\u2019s each with their own unique powers<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092200/extras/Throw.gif?t=1728016255\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/ap